### P4 Agents Relay — Token Budgeting & Analytics
**Status:** Done
**Objective:** G5
**Estimated Duration:** 2 weeks
**Owner:** Tooling Team

**Phase Breakdown:**

| Phase | Task | Owner | Duration | Dependencies | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| P4.1 | TokenBudget and BudgetTracker data model | Tooling | 2 days | D5 | Done |
| P4.2 | Per-step and per-run token tracking | Tooling | 2 days | D5 | Done |
| P4.3 | Budget enforcement: warning, compression, hard-stop | Tooling | 2 days | P4.2 | Done |
| P4.4 | Model escalation fallback on budget exceed | Tooling | 2 days | P4.3 | Done |
| P4.5 | Cost analytics API (per run, per profession, cumulative) | Tooling | 2 days | P4.2 | Done |
| P4.6 | "Savings vs parallel" estimation heuristic | Tooling | 2 days | P4.5 | Done |
| P4.7 | Unit tests for budget enforcement | Tooling | 2 days | P4.3 | Done |

**Risk:** Token counting may differ between API provider reporting and actual billing.  
**Mitigation:** Use API-reported usage where available; warn users that tracked usage is an estimate.

**Depends on:** G5, D5, P2

