### P5 Agents Relay — Frontend Agents View
**Status:** Draft
**Objective:** G5, G6
**Estimated Duration:** 3 weeks
**Owner:** UI Team

**Phase Breakdown:**

| Phase | Task | Owner | Duration | Dependencies | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| P5.1 | Pipeline visualization component (horizontal flow) | UI | 3 days | P2.2 | Empty |
| P5.2 | Run cards with live status and token spend | UI | 2 days | P4.5 | Empty |
| P5.3 | Checkpoint timeline viewer | UI | 2 days | P3.4 | Empty |
| P5.4 | Cost charts (per run, per profession, cumulative) | UI | 2 days | P4.5 | Empty |
| P5.5 | Role/Profession config panel | UI | 2 days | P1.2 | Empty |
| P5.6 | Human gate approval UI (diff view, approve/reject/edit) | UI | 3 days | P2.6 | Empty |
| P5.7 | Run control buttons: pause, resume, rollback, fork | UI | 2 days | P3.5, P3.7, P3.8 | Empty |
| P5.8 | Frontend integration tests | UI | 2 days | P5.1-P5.7 | Empty |

**Risk:** Real-time SSE updates for long-running flows may be unreliable over weak connections.  
**Mitigation:** Use resilient SSE with automatic reconnect; show "last updated at" timestamp.

**Depends on:** G5, G6, P2, P3, P4

